longDescription.value: A boilerplate project housing all of the code that I normally would have copied across to new projects. While it is a work in progress, if you wanted to see how I code, this is a great place to see. This is a mammoth project and I am super proud if it. It's got all sorts of awesome bells and whistles that I typically use in my React-Native projects.

shortDescription.value: A React-Native, Redux and Firebase project.
